## Installation
The application will be available for download on both iOS and Android. 
### Prerequisites
The user just must have a phone capable of running iOS or Android operating system. For the VR capabilities, the user must use an Oculus headset. (WSU ROAR
HAS THESE HEADSETS AT THEIR LOCATION FOR STUDENTS TO USE)
